title: Garen Q bug
body: Not sure if this happens in rift, but on howling abyss. Garen struggles to Q the nexus. He runs around it before he actually lands his q on the nexus

replies.body: I've never been able to duplicate it when I'm recording.  Makes me think I'm crazy...
I've run into this problem on Rift. It seems to be inconsistent though, rarely comes up but when it does it can be a bit annoying.
